### OTLP Logs - JSON format (empty request)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "resourceLogs": []
}

### OTLP Logs - JSON format (single log)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "resourceLogs": [
        {
            "resource": {
                "attributes": [
                    {
                        "key": "service.name",
                        "value": { "stringValue": "my-service" }
                    },
                    {
                        "key": "service.version",
                        "value": { "stringValue": "1.0.0" }
                    }
                ]
            },
            "scopeLogs": [
                {
                    "scope": {
                        "name": "my-library",
                        "version": "1.0.0"
                    },
                    "logRecords": [
                        {
                            "timeUnixNano": "1700000000000000000",
                            "severityNumber": 9,
                            "severityText": "INFO",
                            "body": { "stringValue": "User logged in successfully" },
                            "attributes": [
                                {
                                    "key": "user.id",
                                    "value": { "intValue": "12345" }
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "request.id",
                                    "value": { "stringValue": "abc-123-def" }
                                }
                            ],
                            "traceId": "0102030405060708090a0b0c0d0e0f10",
                            "spanId": "0102030405060708"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}

### OTLP Logs - JSON format (multiple logs with different severity levels)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "resourceLogs": [
        {
            "resource": {
                "attributes": [
                    {
                        "key": "service.name",
                        "value": { "stringValue": "api-gateway" }
                    }
                ]
            },
            "scopeLogs": [
                {
                    "scope": { "name": "http" },
                    "logRecords": [
                        {
                            "timeUnixNano": "1700000000000000000",
                            "severityNumber": 5,
                            "severityText": "DEBUG",
                            "body": { "stringValue": "Request received: GET /api/users" }
                        },
                        {
                            "timeUnixNano": "1700000001000000000",
                            "severityNumber": 9,
                            "severityText": "INFO",
                            "body": { "stringValue": "Request processed successfully" }
                        },
                        {
                            "timeUnixNano": "1700000002000000000",
                            "severityNumber": 17,
                            "severityText": "ERROR",
                            "body": { "stringValue": "Database connection failed" },
                            "attributes": [
                                {
                                    "key": "error.type",
                                    "value": { "stringValue": "ConnectionError" }
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}

